hw1 - Build topology and navigate packets by there types.
hw2 - Load Balancer.
hw3 - Navigate packets in a random topology. 

To install mininet and pox.

Clone the repository
git clone git://github.com/mininet/mininet

cd mininet
git checkout -b 2.2.2
cd ..
mininet/util/install.sh


Some times the controller(POX) remember your previous topology and it can cause problems. So use this:
For cleaning mininet:
sudo mn --clean
